OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FAcclaimed authors have tapped into the
OL,8,FUK's love of crime fiction to help
OL,9,Fexpose how scams work in real life.
OL,11,FCrime writers Clare Mackintosh, Vaseem
OL,12,FKhan and CL (Cally) Taylor have joined
OL,13,Fforces with UK Finance's Take Five to
OL,14,FStop Fraud campaign to create a
OL,15,Ftrilogy of short stories packed with
OL,16,Fplot twists and red herrings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
