OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FAs well as keeping readers guessing,
OL,8,Fthe "read between the lies" stories
OL,9,Fare designed to help protect people
OL,10,Ffrom scams with gripping tales
OL,11,Fexposing the fraud traps that can be
OL,12,Flaid by criminals.
OL,14,FAccording to the campaign, more than
OL,15,F#1.17 billion was recorded stolen
OL,16,Fthrough fraud in 2024, making it a
OL,17,Fcommon crime threat.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
