PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FLaunching for Take Five Week 2026, the
OL,8,Fstories are inspired by real fraud
OL,9,Ftactics and encourage readers to apply
OL,10,Fthe same instincts detectives use in
OL,11,Fcrime books, on television and
OL,12,Fpodcasts to everyday situations.
OL,14,FThe stories include cold callers,
OL,15,Furgent payment requests and situations
OL,16,Fthat may or may not be all they appear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
