FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FThe authors worked with the Dedicated
OL,8,FCard and Payment Crime Unit (DCPCU) to
OL,9,Fhelp them understand how crimes unfold
OL,10,Fin real life, and the emotional impact
OL,11,Fthey have on victims.
OL,13,FEach story focuses on "common and
OL,14,Fdevastating scams". This includes
OL,15,Fromance scams, which resulted in #20.5
OL,16,Fmillion in losses in the first half of
OL,17,F2025, investment scams, with #97.7
OL,18,Fmillion stolen over the same period,
OL,19,Fand impersonation scams, with #45.1
OL,20,Fmillion in losses.
OL,26,@uD@WOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FMs Mackintosh, who is a former Thames
OL,8,FValley Police inspector as well as a
OL,9,Fcrime author, said: "I've seen the
OL,10,Fdevastation caused by fraud, but I've
OL,11,Falso seen the impact crime prevention
OL,12,Fadvice can have.
OL,14,F"Fraud is such a widespread issue `
OL,15,Fand, just like in one of my thrillers,
OL,16,Fspotting it is often about noticing
OL,17,Fthe small clues. This campaign is
OL,18,Fabout helping people slow down,
OL,19,Fquestion what they're being told, and
OL,20,Ffeel more confident spotting when
OL,21,Fsomething isn't right."
OL,26,@qD@UOUvD@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FMr Khan said: "This campaign is close
OL,8,Fto my heart because I've experienced
OL,9,Fimpersonation fraud, so I know just
OL,10,Fhow unsettling it can be.
OL,12,F"I also understand the power of
OL,13,Fstorytelling ` and how we can use it
OL,14,Fto show ordinary people the tactics
OL,15,Fbehind these scams so that they're
OL,16,Fbetter equipped to spot the signs and
OL,17,Fprotect themselves."
OL,26,@oD@OOUtD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FMs Taylor said: "I was really drawn to
OL,8,Fthis campaign because of the power of
OL,9,Fcrime fiction and how much people love
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,F"It's a genre that naturally
OL,13,Fencourages readers to question what's
OL,14,Fhappening and look for clues. Using
OL,15,Fthat instinct to help people
OL,16,Funderstand fraud feels like a really
OL,17,Feffective way to make the advice stick
OL,18,Fand help people feel more confident
OL,19,Fspotting scams."
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
