PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777255442
OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FJess Cook, spokesperson for Take Five
OL,8,Fto Stop Fraud said: "Scammers are
OL,9,Fconstantly evolving their tactics,
OL,10,Fusing increasingly sophisticated
OL,11,Fmethods to catch people off guard and
OL,12,Fexploit trust.
OL,14,F"By partnering with crime writers,
OL,15,Fwe're bringing these tactics to life
OL,16,Fin a way that feels relatable and
OL,17,Fengaging ` helping people recognise
OL,18,Fthe warning signs and reminding them
OL,19,Fthat by stopping, challenging and
OL,20,Fprotecting, they can help prevent
OL,21,Ffraud."
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@AOU}D@GO]
