OL,3,CCrime fiction meets real-world fraud
OL,4,Cas authors help to raise awareness of
OL,5,Cscams
OL,7,FThe short stories are being made
OL,8,Favailable on the Take Five website at
OL,9,Ftakefive-stopfraud.org.uk/read-between-
OL,10,Fthe-lies.
OL,12,FThe Take Five to Stop Fraud campaign
OL,13,Furges people to:
OL,15,FStop ` Some scams are well hidden so
OL,16,Ftake a moment to stop and think.
OL,18,FChallenge ` Ask yourself, could it be
OL,19,Ffake? It is OK to refuse any requests.
OL,20,FOnly criminals will try to rush or
OL,21,Fpanic you.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
